  "id": "RAW_d2b364fb",
  "title": "今日开源（2025-10-28）：CapRL 开源，以解耦两阶段流程 + 75K 问答数据，将强化学习引入开放式图像描述任务",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247500042&idx=1&sn=cc25a59a2bfe12f34802c82821e6373c",
  "date": "2025-10-28 10:44:00",
  "author": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>原创 <span>每日发现最新LLM</span> <span>2025-10-28 18:44</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">中国香港</span></p>\n  <p>3B 图像描述生成器CapRL，基于训练的方法didi-instruct，创新框架UniCode，理论框架Uni_Instruct，基于 Gödel 机器理论的项目HGM，地球观测（EO）Agent框架Earth-Agent</p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=323c1ea3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FGU2ibjU7TDkw4v4yUuC5pA4Xu2WwGdqAXaaC3hMTutThoxpRu6rBVjT8HcrITYEibiaI8wicCaDPA5WFpyD1Dv1NBw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"text-align: center;line-height: normal;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.0859375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;width: 389px;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100010333\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=17b00053&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwuWicsSRFbFewfePZ1EiaVdtFvrJflfNa3P11kpGn8dhrOaAmmKQ3INqCXFZr2IrrUmmtkia9otecsw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif\"></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：CapRL</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5574074074074075\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1156\" data-height=\"644\" data-imgfileid=\"100016380\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=89082224&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkw4v4yUuC5pA4Xu2WwGdqAXvWCQ5ZibSibxGicXLRrbSdaP1ADseoFx4d68us0VdCIKgE8yw9G6amDuw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★CapRL-3B 是一个轻量级的 3B 图像描述生成器，其感知能力可与 Qwen2.5-VL-72B 相媲美。该项目首次将可验证奖励的强化学习应用于开放式和主观的图像描述任务。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">与传统的监督微调不同，CapRL-3B 允许模型探索并生成更广泛的创意和通用描述。项目采用了一个解耦的两阶段训练流程，初始阶段使用大规模视觉语言模型生成丰富且准确的描述，随后通过视觉语言模型进行质量评估。通过使用 CapRL 训练框架和精心筛选的 75K 问答数据集，CapRL-3B 成为一个高效的图像描述生成器。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/caprl\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/caprl</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：didi-instruct</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"724\" data-imgfileid=\"100016378\" data-ratio=\"0.6277777777777778\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1154\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ca9eb37b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkw4v4yUuC5pA4Xu2WwGdqAXcktosX5Fll5vTHtSEJZH1KFBOhVE4t2miblkFc3oiaicaRymszwk4UBGg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Discrete Diffusion Divergence Instruct (DiDi-Instruct) 是一种基于训练的方法，旨在实现快速且高质量的语言生成。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目从预训练的离散扩散语言模型（dLLM）出发，通过</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">蒸馏技术</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">训练出一个快速生成的学生模型。DiDi-Instruct 模型在性能上与其教师模型 dLLM 和 GPT-2 基线相当或更优，并实现了高达 64 倍的加速。其理论基础是基于积分 KL 散度最小化的新框架，提供了实用的训练算法。项目还引入了分组奖励归一化、中间状态匹配和奖励引导的祖先采样器，显著提高了训练稳定性、模型覆盖率和推理质量。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/didi-instruct\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/didi-instruct</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️框架平台、必备工具</span></strong></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：UniCode</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"790\" data-imgfileid=\"100016381\" data-ratio=\"0.6833333333333333\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1156\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ac891ebf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkw4v4yUuC5pA4Xu2WwGdqAXZq7lU6n6ialsEWcMEOqoX29NXPzSSzC3XXZoxHGTSlzTLuP8iaU0ZW5g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★UniCode是一个创新框架，旨在通过自动生成高质量的算法问题和强健的、抗污染的测试用例来解决静态人工编写问题集的局限性。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该框架受到生物进化的启发，通过系统的生成策略创造出多样且具有挑战性的编程问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/unicode\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/unicode</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：Uni_Instruct</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"494\" data-imgfileid=\"100016379\" data-ratio=\"0.42777777777777776\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1156\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b49595b5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkw4v4yUuC5pA4Xu2WwGdqAXycvjbazaUOSs4GkpbibfxMZ1Jd0sycCWXKgdqVx8YFgicWLQtZgPqUzQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Uni-Instruct项目通过统一的扩散发散指令，将超过10种现有的一步扩散蒸馏方法整合在一个理论框架中。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目提出了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">扩散扩展理论</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，解决了原始扩展f-发散的难处理问题，从而有效地训练一步扩散模型。Uni-Instruct不仅在理论上提供了新的贡献，还在CIFAR10和ImageNet-64x64生成基准上实现了创纪录的Frechet Inception Distance (FID)值。此外，该项目还应用于文本到3D生成任务，表现优于之前的方法。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/uni-instruct\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/uni-instruct</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🤖 Agent开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：HGM</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"442\" data-imgfileid=\"100016377\" data-ratio=\"0.3814814814814815\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1160\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3a0b1445&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkw4v4yUuC5pA4Xu2WwGdqAXnOrqkFabbvu4jbkTicuw8IUMVicv2J5XsUpDjnk6k8KAFtLA9fqlL69w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Huxley-Gödel Machine (HGM) 是一个基于 Gödel 机器理论的项目，旨在开发一种理论上最优的自我改进机器。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">HGM 通过编码Agent的方式，使这一概念变得实用。Agent能够通过对整个子树（进化支）的承诺进行估算，来决定哪些自我修改需要扩展。该项目的目标是实现人类水平的编码能力，并通过不断的自我改进来提升性能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/hgm2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/hgm2</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：Earth-Agent</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.375\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1158\" data-height=\"434\" data-imgfileid=\"100016382\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8fbadd41&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkw4v4yUuC5pA4Xu2WwGdqAXbzUQtzPCUHom1m1tUyCVcsNp7NLGJEB330GM7Sg2tnjLFFkAghJmiaw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Earth-Agent是一个地球观测（EO）Agent框架，采用ReAct风格的部分可观测马尔可夫决策过程（POMDP）。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目通过</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">工具调用、记忆更新、审议和行动的循环</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">来解决基于目标和交互历史的任务。Earth-Agent集成了104个专用工具，分为五个功能套件：索引、反演、感知、分析和统计，涵盖感知和光谱分析。项目采用双层协议进行评估，包括最终准确性和轨迹效率的端到端评估，以及工具顺序、工具精确匹配和参数准确性的逐步检查，以表征推理轨迹的完整性和保真度。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/earth-agent2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/earth-agent2</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: center;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-cropselx1=\